下有期徒刑。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/CHDM/110%2c%e7%b0%a1%2c1437%2c20211118%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"CHDM,110,簡,1437,20211118,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"簡","JNO":"1437","JDATE":"20211118","JTITLE":"妨害秩序"}